式，没用项目中的lmdb格式储存数据。我的方式最后拿到的图片是opencv格式，也就是储存在numpy中的。虽然改了resize等针对Image图片格式的操作，但是在训练中loss下降非常缓慢，准确率一直为0。打印出来的预测结果发现基本都是“blank”，后来发现是预处理resizeNormalize类导致图片内容被损坏了。我自己重写了标准化的代码后，问题就解决了。","closed_by":{"login":"HansRen1024","id":26586545,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI2NTg2NTQ1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/26586545?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024","html_url":"https://github.com/HansRen1024","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/HansRen1024/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/issues/213/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Sierkinhane/CRNN_Chinese_Characters_Rec/issues/213/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}